#. * "Trying to use X11 GLX, but EGL is already in use"
#.
#: gdk/gdkglcontext.c:2259
#, c-format
msgid "Trying to use %s, but %s is already in use"
msgstr "Podana je zahteva za uporabo %s, a je %s že v uporabi."

