#: tools/bobgui-rendernode-tool.c:35
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Usage:\n"
"  bobgui4-rendernode-tool [COMMAND] [OPTION…] FILE\n"
"\n"
"Perform various tasks on BOBGUI render nodes.\n"
"\n"
"Commands:\n"
"  benchmark    Benchmark rendering of a node\n"
"  compare      Compare nodes or images\n"
"  convert      Convert into nodes\n"
"  extract      Extract data urls\n"
"  info         Provide information about the node\n"
"  match        Match pattern in the node\n"
"  show         Show the node\n"
"  render       Take a screenshot of the node\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Uporaba:\n"
"  bobgui4-rendernode-tool [UKAZ] [MOŽNOST...] DATOTEKA\n"
"\n"
"Izvajanje različnih opravil z vozlišči izrisovanja BOBGUI.\n"
"\n"
"Ukazi:\n"
"  benchmark    Preizkusno izrisovanje vozlišča\n"
"  compare      Primerja vozlišča ali slike\n"
